%% Diagram: Retry storm feedback loop
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Clients
    participant LB as Load balancer
    participant S as Service
    participant D as Dependency

    Note over S,D: Steady state — latency normal
    C->>LB: 100 req/s
    LB->>S: 100 req/s
    S->>D: 100 req/s
    D-->>S: OK (10 ms)

    Note over D: Dependency degrades
    C->>LB: 100 req/s
    LB->>S: 100 req/s
    S->>D: 100 req/s
    D-->>S: Slow / 5xx
    S-->>LB: Timeout / error

    Note over C,S: Retry without backoff
    C->>LB: +200 retry req/s
    LB->>S: 300 req/s
    S->>D: 300 req/s
    Note over D: Load amplified 3x
    D-->>S: Worse: timeouts cascade
    Note over C,D: Loop continues until <br/> retries exhaust budget or<br/> circuit breaker opens
